  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12px;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">The honeymoon period for MiFID II compliance is officially over. This coupled with the current market turbulence caused by COVID-19 concerns and working from home adds to the reporting complexity. </span></span></p> 
  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12px;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">Even prior to the current market conditions, we have seen an increased demand for regulatory reporting across jurisdictions continue to grow, with organizations relying ever more readily on robust solutions to support their reporting needs. And with that demand now greater than ever before, IHS Markit has created an award-winning solution through our acquisition of Catena Technologies to transform trade reporting. Our best of breed solution solves for the most complex challenges and broad coverage of financial instruments, stringent data quality demands, critical personal data protection requirements, and complex reference data management.</span></span></p> 
  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12px;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">I’d be more than happy to connect with you online, and to walk you through the value of our market-leading capabilities within our best-in-class Integrated Reporting solution. What is a good day/time for you?</span></span></p> 
  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12px;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">In the meantime, please read our <a href="https://ihsmarkit.com/Info/integrated-reporting-case-study-brandywine-global-investment-management.html">case study with Brandywine</a> or watch our recent <a href="https://ihsmarkit.com/info/0520/webinar-best-practices-integrated-regulatory-reporting.html">webinar</a> with Julian Chesser and Struan Lloyd, at IHS Markit, as well as Nick Grist, Head of Regulatory Reporting at SMBC Europe and Dawd Haque, Global Lead for Regulatory Market Initiatives at Deutsche Bank AG. </span></span></p> 
  <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:12px;"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">I look forward to connecting.</span></span></p> 
